{"search_data": "ChhattisgarhChhattisgarh Farm Loan Waiver Scheme \u2013 CG Kisan Karz Mafi Yojana Announced Chhattisgarh new CM Bhupesh Baghel announced CG Farm Loan Waiver Scheme (Kisan Karz Mafi Yojana) to waive off agricultural crop loans of 16.65 lakh farmers taken from cooperative & CG gramin banks, as on 30 November 2018 to a tune of approx. Rs. 6100 crore \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902This announcement about Kisan Karj Mafi Yojana was made while addressing a press conference after he chaired the 1st cabinet meeting of newly formed govt. in the state.Chhattisgarh Farm Loan Waiver Scheme (Kisan Karz Mafi Yojana)The state govt. of Chhattisgarh has announced CG Kisan Karj Mafi Yojana after its 1st cabinet meeting. Under this CG Farm Loan Waiver Scheme, govt. will waive off short term agricultural loans to the tune of around Rs. 6,100 crore of over 16.65 lakh farmers. All the farmers who have taken loans from Cooperative Banks and Chhattisgarh Gramin Banks as on 30 November 2018 would be completely waived.Chhattisgarh Kisan Karz Mafi Yojana will also includes loans of farmers which were taken from commercial banks in the next phase. In the 1st cabinet meeting, CG govt. has decide to raise the Minimum Support Price (MSP) of paddy to Rs. 2,500 per quintal.Cabinet Committee has also took another major decision to form a Special Investigation Team (SIT) to investigate the 2013 case, Jhiram Valley Naxal Attack in Bastar district in which 29 people were killed.\u092a\u0939\u0932\u0940 \u0915\u0948\u092c\u093f\u0928\u0947\u091f \u092e\u0940\u091f\u093f\u0902\u0917 \u0915\u0947 \u0924\u0940\u0928 \u092c\u0921\u093c\u0947 \u092b\u0948\u0938\u0932\u0947 \u20131. 16 \u0932\u093e\u0916 65 \u0939\u091c\u093e\u0930 \u0938\u0947 \u0905\u0927\u093f\u0915 \u0915\u093f\u0938\u093e\u0928\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u093e 6100 \u0915\u0930\u094b\u0921\u093c \u0930\u0942\u092a\u092f\u0947 \u0915\u093e \u0915\u0930\u094d\u091c\u093e \u092e\u093